high_descs: Turn around and go to the right to face the tub.
Pick up the green sponge on the left.
Move to the left and walk around to the other side of the toilet.
Place the green sponge on top of the toilet.
Turn to the right then to left to face the tub again.
Pick up the other green sponge in the tub.
Move to the left and walk around to the other side of the toilet.
Place the green sponge on top of the toilet next to the other one.
anns.task_desc: Place both green sponges on top of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn and move to stand in front of the tub.
Pick up the green sponge closest to the faucet.
Turn left and move to the other side of the toilet, so you're facing the toilet and tub.
Place the sponge in front of the wash cloth on the lid to the tank.
Move back around the toilet to go stand in front of the tub again.
Pick up the other green sponge from the tub.
Turn left and carry the sponge to the other side of the toilet, which puts you standing next to the toilet paper holder.
Place the sponge behind the other sponge on the lid to the tank of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two sponges to the lid of the toilet's tank.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bath tub.
Grab a sponge out of the bath tub
Walk to the toilet on your left.
Place the sponge on the toilet
walk to the bath tub on your right.
Grab the sponge out of the bath tub
Walk to the toilet on your left.
Place the sponge on the toilet next to the first sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place two sponges on top of the toilet.
